Academic Use Notice:
This project was developed as part of the "Smart Space Interactive Programming" 
course at the Department of Interaction Design, National Taipei University of 
Technology. The software is intended for educational and research purposes.

智慧空間互動程式設計課程專案
本軟體為國立臺北科技大學互動設計系「智慧空間互動程式設計」課程專案，
主要用於教育與研究目的。